      What Is a Killing Frost?
    </a>
  </p>

</section>

<section class="card">

  <h2>Not Sure If Your Crop Can Survive an Early Freeze?</h2>

  <p>
    Temperature alone doesn’t determine whether your crop will make it.
    What matters just as much is how close your plants are to maturity.
  </p>

  <p>
    If your tomatoes are nearly ripe, a light frost may not matter.
    But if they still need weeks of growth,
    even one moderate freeze could end the season.
  </p>

